title: The default value set in list box of report parameter is lost after modifying the default value
description: The default value set in the list box of the report parameter is lost after modifying the default value.
OB: No default value is set in the list box of the report parameter.
EB: The default value should be set correctly in the list box of the report parameter.
SR:
1. Open the report parameter settings.
2. Modify the default value of the list box.
3. Check if the default value is set correctly after modification.
